column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.petroR9#_u, p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR9#_i, p.petroR9#_z, gs.lgm_tot_p5# FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObj s ON s.bestobjID = p.objID JOIN galSpecExtra gs ON gs.specobjID = s.specobjID WHERE p.type = # and p.dec > # and p.dec < # and p.ra > # and p.ra < # ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
